as your equal.

489
00:32:27,790 --> 00:32:28,880
Between us,

490
00:32:29,140 --> 00:32:30,670
there is not only equality,

491
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:31,730
but also

492
00:32:32,790 --> 00:32:34,990
love at first sight that lasts forever.

493
00:32:38,470 --> 00:32:41,070
Next month, August 15th,
in the human calendar

494
00:32:41,070 --> 00:32:42,630
will be our wedding day.

495
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:43,810
Is that alright?

496
00:32:46,110 --> 00:32:46,590
Yes.

497
00:32:52,820 --> 00:32:54,270
That's absolutely not acceptable.

498
00:32:54,270 --> 00:32:56,240
How could a human
be worthy of the Azure Dragon?

499
00:32:56,240 --> 00:32:57,240
Yes, Dragon Lord.

500
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:58,640
There has never been

501
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:00,750
a precedent of marriage
between demons and humans.

502
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:02,200
Please reconsider, Dragon Lord.

503
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:06,060
-Please reconsider, Dragon Lord!
-Please reconsider, Dragon Lord!

504
00:33:07,180 --> 00:33:08,040
Dragon Lord...

505
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:13,380
If everything always followed old customs,

506
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:15,030
there would be no Azure Dragon either.

507
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:15,760
Dragon Lord,

508
00:33:16,310 --> 00:33:17,640
you and Hong Ye

509
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,750
