for a short time.

510
00:33:19,750 --> 00:33:22,440
This... things are moving too fast.

511
00:33:22,550 --> 00:33:23,110
-Yes.
-Yes.

512
00:33:23,110 --> 00:33:24,070
Things are moving too fast.

513
00:33:24,070 --> 00:33:25,400
Since when has the depth of love

514
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:27,620
been measured
by the length of acquaintance?

515
00:33:27,620 --> 00:33:28,100
Well...

516
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:30,040
Dragon Lord.

517
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:33,000
I'm afraid a human would marry a dragon

518
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:34,640
just so they can use
the dragon clan's power

519
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:36,500
to help them find the Yuli Spring.

520
00:33:37,480 --> 00:33:38,350
Rumors of this spring

521
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:40,410
has now spread among all demon clans.

522
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:42,550
The claim that Yuli Spring
can enhance cultivation

523
00:33:42,550 --> 00:33:44,070
has caused many demons
to neglect their proper cultivation

524
00:33:44,070 --> 00:33:46,070
and focus only on finding
the celestial mountain.

525
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:48,070
I suspect the Ao Hen Clan
keeps stirring up trouble

526
00:33:48,070 --> 00:33:49,350
and killing other demons

527
00:33:49,350 --> 00:33:51,210
must be connected to this matter.

528
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:54,200
With many issues unresolved
among the demon clans,

529
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:56,800
everyone is waiting for you
to uphold justice.

530
00:33:56,830 --> 00:33:58,790
If you marry a human at this time,

531
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:00,830
it will likely cause unease
among all clans.

532
00:34:00,830 --> 00:34:02,150
Yes, Dragon Lord.

533
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:05,270
If the Dragon Lord doesn't marry Hong Ye,

534
00:34:05,270 --> 00:34:08,000
will everyone
stop seeking the Yuli Spring?

535
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:09,670
Long Yu!

536
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:12,010
Since becoming the Azure Dragon,

537
00:34:12,150 --> 00:34:14,440
our Lord has settled disputes
and protected the weak,

538
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,400
never indulging in luxury,

539
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:17,320
and never acting arrogantly toward anyone.

540
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:18,230
From great demons

541
00:34:18,230 --> 00:34:19,190
down to the flowers and grass,

542
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:20,989
she treats all with utmost care.

543
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:22,960
Just for Long Zhi's tribulation,

544
00:34:23,110 --> 00:34:24,770
she put in tremendous effort.

545
00:34:25,070 --> 00:34:26,030
In my opinion,

546
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:29,400
the Dragon Lord
has never done anything harmful to demons,

547
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:31,199
so we should trust her decision.

548
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:33,630
Secondly, speaking of status,

549
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:35,440
